  • Field Details

    • PROGRESS_FREQUENCY

      protected static final Duration PROGRESS_FREQUENCY
      Defines the frequency at which it is acceptable to log the same message to indicate that the thread is still active. This helps in monitoring the progress and ensuring the thread has not become unresponsive.
